headlines.description: Atalanta snatched a late 2-2 draw away to Napoli amid chaotic scenes on Wednesday as Carlo Ancelotti was sent off amid protests from the hosts.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ancelotti booted in wild Napoli-Atalanta draw

headlines.description: Cristiano Ronaldo converted a stoppage time penalty to give Juventus a last-gasp 2-1 win over Genoa.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ronaldo nets controversial pen as Juve beat Genoa

headlines.description: AS Roma thumped hapless Udinese 4-0 away in Serie A on Wednesday despite playing for nearly an hour with 10 men.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ten-man Roma hit four past leaky Udinese
